{"title":"","uid":"f73a8e23e6f6f669cf99c7dba8fa0722","slug":"阶乘求和","date":"2021-11-27T04:11:23.000Z","updated":"2021-11-27T05:17:39.346Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/阶乘求和.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"阶乘求和问题\"><a href=\"#阶乘求和问题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"阶乘求和问题\"></a><strong>阶乘求和问题</strong></h2><p><strong>题目描述</strong></p>\n<p>求Sn=1!+2!+3!+4!+5!+…+n!之值，其中n是一个数字(n不超过20)。</p>\n<p><strong>输入</strong></p>\n<p>n</p>\n<p><strong>输出</strong></p>\n<p>Sn的值</p>\n<p><strong>样例输入复制</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">5<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>样例输出复制</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">153<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>思路分析：</strong></p>\n<p>题目要求需要求阶乘的和，我们的初步想法是定义一个<strong>求阶乘的递归函数</strong>，再定义一个<strong>主函数</strong>，通过<strong>遍历</strong>，1-n将数字传入fac中，之后 加到sum里。</p>\n<p><strong>注意事项：</strong></p>\n<p>1.采取自定函数求阶乘。用递归法。需注意递归法的尽头。（在本题中，fac函数的if语句作递归法的尽头，不可省略。）</p>\n<p>2.要注意最后结果的数值范围，避免溢出发生错误。</p>\n<p>阶乘很容出现<strong>数值溢出</strong>的问题，所以我们要<strong>扩大数值的存储范围</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">类型名称      字节数  取值范围\nsigned&#96; &#96;char&#96;      &#96;1    -128～+127\nshort&#96; &#96;int&#96;       &#96;2    -32768～+32767\nint&#96;          &#96;4    -2147483648～+2147483647\nlong&#96; &#96;int&#96;       &#96;4    -2147483648～+2141483647\nlong&#96; &#96;long&#96; &#96;int&#96;     &#96;8    -9223372036854775808～+9223372036854775807<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">&#x2F;&#x2F;long int   的简写是   long     占位符是：%ld   \n&#x2F;&#x2F;long long int的简写是   long long   占位符是：%lld<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"代码如下：\"><a href=\"#代码如下：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码如下：\"></a><strong>代码如下：</strong></h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">#include &lt;iostream&gt;\nusing namespace std;\n\n&#x2F;&#x2F;设计的递归函数 返回阶乘值\nlong int fac(int n)&#123;        &#x2F;&#x2F;long int 避免溢出\n\tif(n&#x3D;&#x3D;0)&#123;\n\t\t&#x2F;&#x2F;递归法到尽头 返回1\n\t\treturn 1;\n\t&#125;\n\treturn  (fac(n-1)*n);\n&#125;\n\n&#x2F;&#x2F;主函数\n\nint main()&#123;\n\t&#x2F;&#x2F;思路:先设计一个函数求出每个阶乘\n\tint n;\n\tlong int s&#x3D;0;\n\tcin &gt;&gt; n;\n\tfor(int i&#x3D;1; i&lt;&#x3D;n; i++)&#123;\n\t\ts +&#x3D; fac(i);\n\t&#125;\n\tcout &lt;&lt; s &lt;&lt;endl;\n\treturn 0;\n&#125;\n&#x2F;&#x2F; 时间复杂度O(N)\n&#x2F;&#x2F;空间耗费多 能不用递归就不用递归<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>思路二（首选）：</strong></p>\n<p>我们看第第二次循环的时候也就是2!,此时等于前一个数的阶乘*当前数</p>\n<p> 第三次循环的时候，3!= 2! * 3</p>\n<p> 第四次循环，     4!=3! * 4</p>\n<p> 1*1</p>\n<p>1*2</p>\n<p>1  * 2 *  3</p>\n<p>我们可以退出 </p>\n<p>t *=i;</p>\n<p>s +=t</p>\n<h2 id=\"代码如下\"><a href=\"#代码如下\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码如下\"></a>代码如下</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;\nint main()\n&#123;\n    int n;\n    long long int sum &#x3D; 0, t &#x3D; 1;\n    scanf(&quot;%d&quot;, &amp;n);\n    for (int i &#x3D; 1; i &lt;&#x3D; n; i++)\n    &#123;\n        t *&#x3D; i;\n        sum +&#x3D; t;\n    &#125;\n    printf(&quot;%lld&quot;, sum);\n&#125;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>推荐这个算法，时间复杂度O(n)，但是空间占用小。</p>\n","feature":true,"text":"阶乘求和问题题目描述 求Sn=1!+2!+3!+4!+5!+…+n!之值，其中n是一个数字(n不超过20)。 输入 n 输出 Sn的值 样例输入复制 5 样例输出复制 153 思路分析： 题目要求需要求阶乘的和，我们的初步想法是定义一个求阶乘的递归函数，再定义一个主函数，通过遍历...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.7k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"算法解题","slug":"算法解题","count":2,"path":"api/tags/算法解题.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%98%B6%E4%B9%98%E6%B1%82%E5%92%8C%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\"><span class=\"toc-text\">阶乘求和问题</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">代码如下：</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">代码如下</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"一只菜狗","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"大概是还不够优秀，还不值得拥有。","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{"title":"心得","uid":"d99beffd6d18fcf284cf84edd552f486","slug":"心得","date":"2021-11-23T16:15:45.000Z","updated":"2021-11-23T16:17:47.298Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/心得.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"1 读书心得 1.推荐书《硅谷之火》 2.上大学重要的不是学习知识，而是学会如何学习知识，重要的主动学习的方法和技能。 3.大学生不适合刚开始就直接创业，因为缺乏行业经验，就算勉强做成，对于长久发展来说，也不算优势。ps：积累编程经验，互联网知识，多实践。 4.要有胆量去想，想好...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":234,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"心得","slug":"心得","count":1,"path":"api/tags/心得.json"}],"aut